items.name: STATISTIC
lines: A possible value for column TYPE in the com.sun.star.sdbc.XResultSet object returned by the method com.sun.star.sdbc.XDatabaseMetaData.getIndexInfo().
Identifies table statistics that are returned in conjunction with a table's index description.

items.name: CLUSTERED
lines: A possible value for column TYPE in the com.sun.star.sdbc.XResultSet object returned by the method com.sun.star.sdbc.XDatabaseMetaData.getIndexInfo().
Indicates that this table index is a clustered index.

items.name: HASHED
lines: A possible value for column TYPE in the com.sun.star.sdbc.XResultSet object returned by the method com.sun.star.sdbc.XDatabaseMetaData.getIndexInfo().
Indicates that this table index is a hashed index.

items.name: OTHER
lines: A possible value for column TYPE in the com.sun.star.sdbc.XResultSet object returned by the method com.sun.star.sdbc.XDatabaseMetaData.getIndexInfo().
Indicates that this table index is not a clustered index, a hashed index, or table statistics; it is something other than these.
